{
  "id": "RAW_2cebce90",
  "title": "苹果×谷歌：AI 世纪联姻正式宣布，谷歌一夜市值突破 4 万亿刀！苹果底层全上 Gemini，马斯克警告：谷歌权力太集中了！网友：老马快造手机吧",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODI5Njc2MA==&mid=2655935350&idx=1&sn=720929250ecdf108b88aa6e199a52c58",
  "date": "2026-01-13 04:58:00",
  "author": "51CTO技术栈",
  "siteName": "51CTO技术栈",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/MOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTAyDj7grJU5ibZClqoAv8HRWQWJ4VOLtKffIB5cLRicAYrmXChrOSJ7Kgw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"239\" data-imgfileid=\"508451665\" data-ratio=\"0.4255937954435288\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"2063\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8cbbba0f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTAyDj7grJU5ibZClqoAv8HRWQWJ4VOLtKffIB5cLRicAYrmXChrOSJ7Kgw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"149\" data-end=\"261\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">编辑 | 云昭</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"149\" data-end=\"261\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌一夜之间，市值首次突破了4万亿美元了！</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"149\" data-end=\"261\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">起因则是一段让科技圈炸裂的新闻。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"149\" data-end=\"261\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"161\" data-end=\"202\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">苹果与谷歌正式宣布达成一项多年期深度合作协议</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，称：下一代苹果基础模型将会基于谷歌的Gemini模型和云技术，包括未来的Apple Intelligence、以及今年即将推出的个性化Siri。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508451651\" data-ratio=\"1.1478260869565218\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"690\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0e832feb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTAyo8eibSiacPKibjB1LzLc4vH5lmockRPiaZYAjic3ALRoXhkdBTLkiaXURUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"331\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这条消息直接冲上了各大科技媒体头条，也引发了行业大佬的震动和争议。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"331\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">一方面是，市场终于看到苹果AI问世的新希望：背后基于谷歌Gemini，新升级的Siri终于</span></span><strong data-start=\"290\" data-end=\"330\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">要彻底进化了，虽然它的大脑是来自于竞争对手。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"331\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一位AI圈的工程师表示，这或许是正确的做法，但如果苹果基础模型都是基于Gemini微调，还能成为“苹果基础模型”吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"331\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508451657\" data-ratio=\"0.6063348416289592\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"663\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=35855fda&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTAFOlGJ9IvNmVe5x81PqvXtDIBGl5MjLjYnwOSWGet2ib1oFF1HO4pzFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"331\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">马斯克直接开怼：别忘了谷歌还有安卓和Chrome浏览器，谷歌的“权力垄断”有些不合理。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508451656\" data-ratio=\"0.4798206278026906\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"669\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ecf32363&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTAqKZcLFBxy0gwljnB4B6nxnb5loUWaj4mq3htGkvArh1iaTWlb5JpcaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"331\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;263&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;331&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为此，有网友呼吁：老马，你还是自己造一款&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">𝕏</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Phone吧！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508451658\" data-ratio=\"0.9726027397260274\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"657\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bd9b546b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTApRuCuRASCib4amnBL1o2uH4J6TBtJd7P5GKCrKSNqvicdiczmxLlQFLuw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"331\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">两大被视为竞争对手的宣布联盟，的确有很多叙事，这就带大家梳理一下。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"338\" data-end=\"364\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong data-start=\"344\" data-end=\"364\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">这次合作，双方都强调了什么？</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"192\" data-end=\"359\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"192\" data-end=\"209\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">首先，双方都强调，这是一项为期多年深度合作协议。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"192\" data-end=\"359\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"192\" data-end=\"209\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据联合声明，苹果未来的基础 AI 模型将基于谷歌的 Gemini 模型与云技术构建</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。这标志着双方从传统的搜索引擎合作向更深层的&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"308\" data-end=\"321\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI 技术合作迈进</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"235\" data-end=\"250\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;\">ps：从第一代 iPhone 开始，苹果和谷歌就有一项长达至今的搜索引擎合作。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"254\" data-end=\"282\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"254\" data-end=\"282\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;\">Safari 浏览器的默认搜索引擎：Google。Spotlight 搜索、Siri 的搜索结果，也长期优先走 Google。作为交换，谷歌则需要每年向苹果支付一笔丰厚的“分成费用”，大概是150亿~200亿美元/年。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"192\" data-end=\"359\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而这次的合作模式，是否依旧会延续上面提到的“广告分成”，目前还没有得到确切的消息。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">不过有网友猜测：100亿刀？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508451660\" data-ratio=\"0.4315068493150685\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"584\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b33901b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTABEBemZ8uKOzRLcNkh03ek3sulyribVkB2Ba2xLj4HVq9usbIicHoLGAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"361\" data-end=\"515\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"361\" data-end=\"379\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">其次，Siri 迎来关键升级，Geimini成新大脑。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"361\" data-end=\"515\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"361\" data-end=\"379\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">苹果计划利用谷歌的 Gemini 模型进行&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong data-start=\"404\" data-end=\"422\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">下一代 Siri 重建与增强</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，预计将于&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"428\" data-end=\"442\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2026 年晚些时候</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;推出。这意味着 Siri 将具备更强的理解、上下文推理和智能交互能力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">（前两年，苹果还曾宣布要引入OpenAI的ChatGPT来升级Siri，不过OpenAI并没有公开回应此事。）</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"517\" data-end=\"677\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"517\" data-end=\"549\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">第三，Apple Intelligence 平台将被强化。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不仅是 Siri，苹果的</span></span></strong><strong data-start=\"564\" data-end=\"595\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Apple Intelligence 整体 AI 功能</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也将借助 Gemini 提升底层能力，让设备表现出更强的智能交互、语言理解与情境感知能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"679\" data-end=\"819\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"679\" data-end=\"695\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">最后，苹果强调：合作并非把控制权交给谷歌。有消息称，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">尽管技术底层来自谷歌，苹果公开强调，这一合作而是</span></span></strong><strong data-start=\"718\" data-end=\"735\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在“幕后技术支持”层面进行</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：Gemini 模型通过 Apple 的私有云计算或设备端运行，</span></span><strong data-start=\"767\" data-end=\"781\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不会直接触及用户数据。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"366\" data-end=\"386\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <p data-start=\"731\" data-end=\"856\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;731&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;856&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，用户数据不会被谷歌直接访问。这是苹果在合作细节上刻意凸显的一点。</span></span></p>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong data-start=\"1492\" data-end=\"1513\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">苹果为何最后选择了谷歌AI？</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1515\" data-end=\"1536\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其实，这次多年的联盟合作宣布，并非偶然。这背后也是苹果追赶竞争对手的最佳选择。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1538\" data-end=\"1569\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">首先，众所周知，自ChatGPT爆火后的三年以来，</span></span><strong data-start=\"1547\" data-end=\"1569\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Siri 的 AI 整体表现长期落后。</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1570\" data-end=\"1729\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比竞争对手（如 ChatGPT、Claude、Gemini 本身的表现），Siri 一直被诟病为“反应迟钝、理解能力弱”。（尤其是WWDC2024，推出的Apple Intelligence，让不少圈内人士大感失望，难掩苹果内部延误的AI节奏。）</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1570\" data-end=\"1729\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当然，苹果内部依旧没有彻底放弃自研基础模型，但奈何在规模和性能上并未形成明显优势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508451661\" data-ratio=\"1.081896551724138\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"696\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=878db52f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTACrBmeznChWJbRe2CYXPpqFEHjsQNtBNhXHt6Hqfb5tSS1yMK7r45HA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1570\" data-end=\"1729\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;1515&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;1536&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">既然短期打不过，不如握手谈合作。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1731\" data-end=\"1755\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"1740\" data-end=\"1755\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其次，苹果需要依赖于最强大的AI基础设施，来构建统一的智能设备体验。</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1756\" data-end=\"1907\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如今，智能助手、智能搜索、语音交互正在成为现代操作系统的标配。作为原生全模态的最强前沿模型，Gemini被苹果选中，也是在意料之中。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1756\" data-end=\"1907\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着未来 iPhone、iPad、Mac、Vision Pro 等设备的智能体验将更统一、更强大。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1756\" data-end=\"1907\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，苹果并没有丢弃多供应链策略。虽然引入了谷歌，但苹果仍强调不会放弃与其他 AI 合作伙伴（如 OpenAI）的关系——后者目前在复杂语义生成场景中仍有所补充。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1935\" data-end=\"2073\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这表明苹果在 AI 路线上的思路依旧是是“多模型供给 + 自主体验构建”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"731\" data-end=\"856\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">谷歌市值首破 4 万亿，美股见证历史性一刻</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"904\" data-end=\"1025\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">恰逢2026开年，两大巨头在新一波科技浪潮之上达成多年合作。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"904\" data-end=\"1025\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此举释放出的信号立刻反映到了资本市场：谷歌母公司 Alphabet 的市值一度突破&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"948\" data-end=\"958\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">4 万亿美元</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，创下历史新高。投资者将这看作是谷歌 AI 领先优势的体现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508451653\" data-ratio=\"0.822463768115942\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"828\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1df612a9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTAMOJXpYiaLFokYGD1WZlk7yqib7VTSRSIY2bcMJ0McXuqSkt0IYWrKrlQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1027\" data-end=\"1075\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而苹果的股价则相对来说稳中略涨，这也表明市场对苹果自研 AI 能力存在疑虑，或认为此次合作是补短板的务实之举。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8491189427312775\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"908\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"508451654\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d1af9226&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTA4ia6bbPxIHNlBU3YhvzdACibSYS2Ry4H1PHNf3bHkia1ooszcRNw38Xew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"1082\" data-end=\"1109\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong data-start=\"1088\" data-end=\"1109\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">二阶影响：马斯克公开表达担忧，或影响AI竞争格局</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"1111\" data-end=\"1281\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">消息发布数小时后，</span></span><strong data-start=\"1120\" data-end=\"1151\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">马斯克随即在评论区发声，直指这次合作可能带来“权力过度集中”的风险。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1111\" data-end=\"1281\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"1120\" data-end=\"1151\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">言外之意，这样的合作可能过度强化谷歌在 AI 基础设施和生态中的统治地位，尤其考虑到谷歌同时还控制 Android、Chrome 等关键入口。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1283\" data-end=\"1292\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">很明显，马斯克的担忧是有必要的。毕竟，谷歌实在是太强大。一旦二者在手机上达成AI基础设施方面的合作，很多“二阶影响”都不得重新考虑。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1295\" data-end=\"1340\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"1295\" data-end=\"1307\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">市场权力过度集中</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：谷歌在 AI、操作系统、浏览器等多条赛道的影响力可能进一步加深；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1343\" data-end=\"1386\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"1343\" data-end=\"1353\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">竞争格局变化</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：随着苹果采用竞争对手的核心技术，AI 生态可能出现更少的选择性；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1389\" data-end=\"1426\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"1389\" data-end=\"1401\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">隐私与控制权问题</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：即使数据不被共享，底层技术依赖可能带来长期影响。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1428\" data-end=\"1479\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">马斯克的评论引起行业高度关注，甚至有人认为，与其说这是一次技术合作，倒不如说更像是一场围绕“AI 主导权”展开的博弈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"508451659\" data-ratio=\"0.2350230414746544\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"651\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=31f67d3e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQomoV2KpQqsHQz0GCNUtGTAxica7s9IdGm4mRlsNQJibgGUWjo4d0z4cn0xicicCdBqkcZ3adSrnqOX5Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"2080\" data-end=\"2104\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong data-start=\"2086\" data-end=\"2104\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">结语：技术合作还是行业重构？</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2262\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无论如何，这次苹果与谷歌的合作，是硅谷 AI 竞争格局中一个非常关键的节点。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2262\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">小编看来，这场两大科技巨头在AI上达成“世纪联姻”，影响将不低于一个新版本的GPT发布。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2262\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">短期来看，很显然，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">它将首先</span></span><strong data-start=\"2151\" data-end=\"2192\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">实质性提升 Siri 与 Apple Intelligence 的智能水平，今年我们很快就要和一个已经得到大众认可的最强模型作为基座的IPhone和Siri了。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2262\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果我们把视角拉长一年，我们期待已久的“AI原生手机”，到底体验如何，也许就会有一个真正的苹果版答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2262\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而如果时间再拉长一些，谷歌一旦进入了苹果手机的智能核心层，马斯克的那个担忧，同时恰恰也是一个新时代的预警：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2262\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">接下来，AI 基础设施层面的生态平衡终将打破重构，而这个天平，或已经向谷歌开始倾斜。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2262\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">国外的谷歌、OpenAI、Anthropic，国内的大模型六小龙，DeepSeek、Qwen、豆包、Kimi、文心一言……相信不久将会迎来一番新的生态叙事。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2262\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">就在刚刚，Anthropic 今晚就发了一款新产品Cowork，办公版的ClaudeCode，扩大了自己的生态版图。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2262\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">且拭目以待吧！</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "苹果与谷歌正式宣布达成多年期深度 AI 合作，未来苹果底层 AI 如 Siri 和 Apple Intelligence 将基于谷歌 Gemini 模型及云技术，引发市场震动及马斯克对权力集中的担忧。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "苹果与谷歌正式宣布达成多年期深度 AI 合作，未来苹果底层 AI 如 Siri 和 Apple Intelligence 将基于谷歌 Gemini 模型及云技术，引发市场震动及马斯克对权力集中的担忧。",
  "summary": "苹果和谷歌正式宣布达成一项多年期深度 AI 合作协议，苹果未来的基础模型，包括 Apple Intelligence 和 Siri，将基于谷歌的 Gemini 模型和云技术。此消息立即推动谷歌市值突破 4 万亿美元，反映市场对其 AI 领先地位的认可。合作旨在升级苹果长期受诟病的 Siri 的智能水平，并构建统一的智能设备体验，但苹果强调用户数据不会被谷歌直接访问。此次合作引发了行业大佬的广泛关注，马斯克公开表达担忧，认为这可能导致谷歌权力过度集中，影响 AI 竞争格局。文章分析了苹果选择谷歌的原因，并讨论了此次合作对 AI 生态和行业重构的深远影响。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "苹果与谷歌达成多年期深度 AI 合作，苹果底层 AI 将集成谷歌 Gemini。",
      "explanation": "此次合作将使 Siri 和 Apple Intelligence 等苹果核心 AI 功能，基于谷歌的 Gemini 模型和云技术进行构建和强化，标志着两家公司从传统搜索引擎合作向更深层 AI 技术合作迈进。"
    },
    {
      "point": "合作助推谷歌市值创新高，市场看好其 AI 主导地位。",
      "explanation": "消息宣布后，谷歌母公司 Alphabet 市值一度突破 4 万亿美元，显示资本市场对谷歌 AI 领先优势的强烈认可和对此次合作的积极预期。"
    },
    {
      "point": "苹果选择谷歌 AI 系弥补自身 Siri 短板并建立统一智能体验。",
      "explanation": "面对 Siri 长期落后的局面，苹果选择与最强大的 AI 基础设施合作，旨在快速提升其设备的智能体验，但仍保留与其他 AI 伙伴建立多模型供给关系的策略。"
